column1: Dataset name: ESA95 National Accounts; Frequency: Quarterly; Adjustment indicator: Neither seasonally nor working day adjusted; Use or asset sector: Total economy including Rest of the World (all sectors); ESA95 account: Gross domestic product at market prices; Resource or liability sector: Total economy; ESA95 breakdown: Total; Nat accounts price reference: Chain linked; Series unit - ESA95 context: National currency; Series suffix - ESA95 context: Main series
